# the definition
@DEFN=A specialized {Patricia tree} whose {internal nodes} store only
an integer, $k$, which is the length of the common {prefix} of the
strings in the {children#child}.  Equivalently, the strings first
differ in the $(k+1)<sup>st</sup>$ character.
