Used in a specialized algorithm, described in <em>Engineering a
Lightweight Suffix Array Construction Algorithm</em>, to build {suffix
arrays}.
</p>

<p>
The name comes from re<strong>TRIE</strong>val and is
pronounced, "tree".  See the historical note at {trie}.

